Name: Chests, City, Clicker
About the game: Chests, City, Clicker allows you to open chests, build a city and click. What more do you need? Probably a second monitor so as not to get bored. In this game, you can build and upgrade more buildings to expand your city! There are no wrong decisions, whatever you do - you will get even richer! Don't wait, just click! The game includes: - 17 characters with their own short story - 4 buildings - Shop with changing offers - Chests everywhere (instant gratification) - Scalable quests If you have nothing to do with your time, this is the perfect game for you!
